entry.title: Seshat Results
entry.summary: Seshat Ommited Results This page accompanies a submission to TOSEM, “Predictive Mutation Analysis via Natural Language Channel in Source Code”. In this supplementary page, we have listed the figures and tables omitted from the submission due to their redundancy considering readability. In the original paper, we focused on reporting F-scores as precisions and recalls have shown similar patterns.
